# WebAuthn / FIDO2 Implementation Status

## Completed

### Backend (Go)
- [x] `apps/api/internal/db/migrations/007_webauthn.sql` ΓÇö Database schema for webauthn_credentials, registration_sessions, login_sessions
- [x] `apps/api/internal/auth/webauthn.go` ΓÇö Core WebAuthn service using `github.com/go-webauthn/webauthn`
  - User and credential models implementing library interfaces
  - Begin/Finish registration with challenge/session storage
  - Begin/Finish login with session management
  - Credential CRUD (list, delete, rename, lookup by raw ID)
  - Backup eligibility, resident key, and user verification support
  - Configurable registration/login options (platform/roaming, resident key preference)
- [x] `apps/api/internal/auth/webauthn_handlers.go` ΓÇö HTTP handlers
  - `POST /api/v1/auth/webauthn/register/begin`
  - `POST /api/v1/auth/webauthn/register/finish`
  - `POST /api/v1/auth/webauthn/login/begin`
  - `POST /api/v1/auth/webauthn/login/finish`
  - `GET /api/v1/auth/webauthn/credentials`
  - `DELETE /api/v1/auth/webauthn/credentials/:id`
  - `PATCH /api/v1/auth/webauthn/credentials/:id`
- [x] `apps/api/internal/api/handlers/webauthn.go` ΓÇö Handler package wrapper
- [x] `apps/api/internal/api/router.go` ΓÇö Routes wired for all endpoints
- [x] `apps/api/config/config.go` ΓÇö Added WebAuthn RP config fields

